library(ggplot2)
peri.plot <- ggplot(embryos, aes(x= Litter.Theiler.stage,y=perimeter..m.,shape = Naa10.genotype))+
  geom_point(aes(shape = Naa10.genotype))+
     geom_boxplot(outlier.shape = NA,
               alpha = 0.1)+
    stat_summary(fun = mean, color = "black", position = position_dodge(0.75),width = 0.2,
             geom = "crossbar",
             show.legend = FALSE)+
   geom_errorbar(data = peri.summ, aes(ymin=perimeter..m.-sd,
                     ymax=perimeter..m.+sd),
                 width=.2,
                 position=position_dodge(0.75))+
  xlab("Theiler stage of litter")+
  ylab("perimeter (m)")+
  ggtitle("Embryo perimeter during development")+
  theme_bw(base_size = 12, base_family = "Helvetica")
